{"tid":1784894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社福界明起罷工三日","createTime":"2019-12-16T04:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T03:07:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c9a019b2460ad12dafa19eaff68672bece4e30","tid":1784894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/UEUOHLKNAN7THGTGT75CQEZN6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FUEUOHLKNAN7THGTGT75CQEZN6E%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=ab94eee4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FUEUOHLKNAN7THGTGT75CQEZN6E%2F&h=a8463ae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/UEUOHLKNAN7THGTGT75CQEZN6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n社福界明起罷工三日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576425931_8a57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576425931_8a57.jpg&h=4e99674d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社福界近500人昨在中環愛丁堡廣場舉行造勢大會，為一連三日罷工行動明志。董立華攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中抗爭持續逾半年，多名社工因在示威現場協助被捕人士遭拘捕。社福界計劃明起一連三日發動警告式罷工，要求政府盡快回應五大訴求。社福界罷工委員會昨率先舉行造勢大會，近500人參加。有前線社工期望罷工行動能帶動其他行業加入罷工行列。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民籲罷食藍店：一啖一滴細路血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「大人肯罷工 細路唔使衝」<br />\n<br />\n造勢大會在中環愛丁堡廣場舉行。早前被控暴動的陣地社工、社福界罷工委員會委員陳虹秀表示，自己曾看見參與示威的學生將遺書放在身上，對年輕人準備為港犧牲感沉重，社福界同工不希望再有年輕人犧牲，故決定以罷工道德感召社會其他界別參與抗爭，「大人肯罷工，細路唔使衝」。<br />\n<br />\n社福界服務受惠者譚太發言時指，雖然罷工會為她帶來不便，但表示諒解。她亦認同罷工是迫使政府回應民意方式，「𠵱家個政府充耳不聞」。<br />\n<br />\n理大包圍戰中被捕社工黎柏然發言時稱，早前拘留期間，遇上以前一個品學兼優學生，對方問黎會否對他失望，黎聽後感痛心，「我答佢，我無資格失望，我哋一齊行」。他憶述當時在理大內留守的年輕人都活在恐慌中，但社工只能用謊言安撫他，「我拍佢膊頭時，自己隻手都震」。他期望透過罷工表達「社工唔係維穩機器」的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n集會最後展示一幅寫上「社福界罷」的巨型橫額明志。發言人曾紀南估計，有40個機構工會或關注組共2,000名社福界員工參與罷工，部份非緊急支援服務或會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅智堅"},{"pid":"a70079d846b87acaff004d5a4b5f8ddb9530972d","tid":1784894,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6aa80a2792da3bfc18ca42d5b2e48ff126985e8","tid":1784894,"uid":27946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9604701c96457a54b4325e08e1dcfecf135cd9","tid":1784894,"uid":186276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2888b5d6203660146275d667efb9d8099037cf72","tid":1784894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxUG26w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxUG26w.jpg&h=5e518208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boyz9mA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fboyz9mA.jpg&h=681d4c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpGueC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpGueC9.jpg&h=2c51b16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6186423fac50a324373aff1a9ab36394dd7f2f1","tid":1784894,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T